{"id": 2344, "genre": 1000, "title": "亲密关系中，你是哪种道歉人格？", "description": "和家人/朋友/对象争吵后要重归于好，你都会选择什么方式？（题图来自：视觉中国）", "record_count": 12531, "comment_count": 31, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180514162828d2IJM49SGl8LN5iP.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-05-17T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4174, "title": "亲密关系中，你是哪种道歉人格？", "content": "亲密关系中，你是哪种道歉人格？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 281720, "content": "送小礼物型，说不出口的话就赔个礼", "image": "img/option/option/20180514163008DvCXfkVEmtQxrdR2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 281722, "content": "让步道歉型，主动先打破僵局", "image": "img/option/option/20180514163706Goq9QNUDa7tjfcJB.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 281727, "content": "理性复盘沟通型，为了避免重蹈覆辙有必要好好唠唠", "image": "img/option/option/20180514164240X6eb71lmDdquYkEr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 281729, "content": "当做没事型，冷静下来后让时间化解是最好的方法", "image": "img/option/option/20180514164417TJrfR1lGPt0EVZiv.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 281730, "content": "曲线救国型，找亲友来中间调和有时很管用", "image": "img/option/option/201805141647287buctSDvPjCmFhQW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 281731, "content": "邀约活动型，和对方一起吃饭运动总有助于感情修复", "image": "img/option/option/20180514164932MZj0r6vp3ETYFJKi.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 281732, "content": "逗笑对方型，驱散愤怒的方法就是换个情绪", "image": "img/option/option/20180514165016LdkUtlKrza0Osy5P.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 281733, "content": "自己没错的话绝对不妥协型，等对方道歉时再原谅ta", "image": "img/option/option/20180514165114n8pX40CKAQktjwbL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}